<p>In addition to having all the benefits of the original Alpha Consumer Card, The Alpha Consumer Platinum Card has up to 22,7 % higher bonus rates for most* buys. As if that&#8217;s not reason enough to acquire the Alpha Consumer Platinum Card, there is one exclusive benefit that will knock your socks off and even clean them for you and put them folded back in your drawer.</p>
