<p>&nbsp;<br />
Alpha Consumer Services has developed a revolutionary new system called SAFE (Secured Acquired Finance Establishment). This system allows your money to be transferred directly to the local ACS Bank as you swipe your card for purchase, and then immediately transferred again to an overseas bank account where it buys stock options in ACS for the amount of your original purchase, thereby removing the trace back to your account.</p>
<p>In return ACS will then buy the selected item(s) for you, in ASC&#8217;s name, by transffering the allotted amount to the terminal at which you first made your purchase. You can now leave with your newly acquired goods and the only trace of this is a transfer of money to your local ACS Bank where its statement will read once a month &#8220;Platinum Membership Fee [given month]&#8221;.</p>
<p><small><em>* this includes such items as ammunition, guns, knives, protective clothing, all bathroom equipment, all cleaning items and even some shoes and boots.</em></small></p>
